title: Updated version number in the manifest file
message: Updated version number in the manifest file

title: Updated vibration cancellation to only happen when the screen is turned
message:
Updated vibration cancellation to only happen when the screen is turned
off, and made some spelling correction

title: Updated message cancellation for vibrate to one screen change
message:
Updated message cancellation for vibrate to one screen change
(previously, hitting the power button once would silence the vibrator
and not stop the service (might confuse the end user))

title: Added about page and morse code translation chart page. Added action bar
message:
Added about page and morse code translation chart page. Added action bar
to link these pages along with appropriate icons. Commented out all
google analytics code (save for future release). Updated message
cancelling to hitting the power button twice.

title: Added google analytics tracking to MainActivity.java and
message:
Added google analytics tracking to MainActivity.java and
SmsMorseCodeService.java, updated XML files to remove warnings

title: Refactored and documented MainActivit.java. Refactored and documented
message:
Refactored and documented MainActivit.java. Refactored and documented
SmsMorseCodeReceiver.java. Removed unused permissions from
AndroidManifest.xml. Changed logo color to match the main activity
layout color, and replace "SMS" with "SOS" within logo (with "SMS"
people will likely think I incorrectly translated "SOS").

title: Removed text to speech so translation is pure morse code. Removed
message:
Removed text to speech so translation is pure morse code. Removed
ability to stop audio track on volume down. Added ACTION_SCREEN_OFF
broadcast receiver for stopping service when power button is used to
turn screen off. Now playing audiotrack in a thread

title: Refactored Constants.java. Changed toggle button from "on/off" to
message:
Refactored Constants.java. Changed toggle button from "on/off" to
"enabled/disabled". Refactored activity_main.xml.

title: Changed name from SMSMorseCode to SMorSe for a better fit beneath the
message:
Changed name from SMSMorseCode to SMorSe for a better fit beneath the
icon. Change the name of the service from MyService.java to
SmsMorseCodeService.java

title: Refactored the MorseCodeConverter.java class and added documentation.
message:
Refactored the MorseCodeConverter.java class and added documentation.
Added support for all characters in the ITU-R recommendation. Removed
the MorseCodeVibrateConvert.java class (no longer used)

title: Split the MorseCodeTrack class into two separate classes,
message:
Split the MorseCodeTrack class into two separate classes,
MorseCodeAudioTrack, and MorseCodeVibrateTrack. Refactored and
documented each of these classes. The MorseCodeAudioTrack class handles
audio play back of the body of the text message, and the
MorseCodeVibrateTrack class handles vibration play back of the morse
code message. Made changes to MyService to accommodate the new classes.
Removed the SoundService class as it was not being used.

title: Refactored the MyService class, and added accurate documentation
message:
Refactored the MyService class, and added accurate documentation
Added a releaseTrack method to the MorseCodeTrack class that releases
the morseCode AudioTrack when called
